{
  "texts": [
    "Although both humans and now AI make coherent meaning from the endless combinatorial possibilities of language, they have fundamentally different mechanisms for taming these infinities.",
    "Multimodal MeaningGenerative AI is essentially a technology of written text.",
    "Only derivatively is it multimodal (Cope and Kalantzis 2023c, Munn, Magee and Arora 2023a).",
    "Take images, for instance.",
    "The resource for image generation is billions of digitized images."
  ]
}